data.description: Come tour this beautiful one story home in the Willow Forest subdivision.  It has large living spaces that afford plenty of space for entertaining. The attractive kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, a breakfast den and a double oven. The garage has been converted into an extra large living area (guest suite) with its own bathroom, and an office style flex space (or small nursery). On the other side of the enclosed atrium you will find two more bedrooms with a full bathroom to share. Tucked away at the end of the hallway is the large private master suite with its en suite bathroom, walk in closet, and personal side patio that leads to the backyard.  Newer Hardy siding throughout, Newer HVCA system and a whole home filtration system all paid off. Convenient location with easy access to 99 making it a breeze to go anywhere in Houston. FHA assumable loan with low interest rate.   PRICE DROP!
